activities:
Connectyard is an engagement platform operating in the education technology market.  Connectyard extends the functionality of learning management systems and e-books by providing notification services to better engage students, faculty, and staff with educational content.  To facilitate this activity, the following personal information is collected:

User name - provides a recognizable identifier for notifications regarding end-user;
User email - provides a unique identifier to organize messaging. Also used as channel for notification;
Course ID - allows messaging for groups to be properly organized;
Course name - provides a recognizable identifier for group messaging.
Phone - necessary for SMS notification channel.
